      "span_text": "All birds had previously taken part in experiments involving tooluse and learning object properties, and some had taken part in a cooperative study with conspecifics (light blue, D3R, D4R, D4B and RWY  ), but no subjects had ever been required to attend to human actions or the movement of rewards."
